      },
      {
        "start": "00:02.800",
        "end": "00:05.400",
        "original": "探しに行く",
        "english": "We go to find it",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:05.800",
        "end": "00:11.000",
        "original": "スカートはラウンドだって",
        "english": "Our skirts go round and round",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:32.400",
        "end": "00:36.800",
        "original": "まだ 独り言 続いた",
        "english": "My monologue still continued",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:37.300",
        "end": "00:41.600",
        "original": "ただ 始めたくて 走った",
        "english": "I ran, just wanting to start",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:42.100",
        "end": "00:46.600",
        "original": "遠く 暗がりに 灯った",
        "english": "A light in the distant darkness",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:47.000",
        "end": "00:51.400",
        "original": "それは 眩しすぎた 名前",
        "english": "It was a name far too bright",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:52.300",
        "end": "00:56.800",
        "original": "それは 優しすぎる 思い出",
        "english": "They are memories far too kind",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:57.100",
        "end": "00:59.800",
        "original": "もっと 近づけと 手を伸ばした",
        "english": "I reached out to get closer",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:00.700",
        "end": "01:03.000",
        "original": "思いがけず 結び合った",
        "english": "We unexpectedly joined hands",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:03.200",
        "end": "01:07.400",
        "original": "ほら 今 迷い子は 僕らになった",
        "english": "Look, now the lost children have become us",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:08.500",
        "end": "01:12.800",
        "original": "パレパレパレ 輝くんだよ",
        "english": "Parade, parade, parade, let's shine",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:13.300",
        "end": "01:17.800",
        "original": "悔しさも 愛しさも 全て おいで",
        "english": "Regrets and affection, bring them all along",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:18.500",
        "end": "01:22.800",
        "original": "風 夢 羽 飛び立てるさ",
        "english": "With wind, dreams, and wings, we can take flight",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:23.200",
        "end": "01:26.500",
        "original": "ささやかな 祝いの光",
        "english": "A small light of celebration",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:27.000",
        "end": "01:29.000",
        "original": "終わりなき 日差し",
        "english": "Endless sunlight",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:29.400",
        "end": "01:33.700",
        "original": "君を見つけたこと 胸を張れるよ",
        "english": "Finding you is something I can be proud of",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:34.200",
        "end": "01:38.800",
        "original": "ここから これから Our Bright Parade",
        "english": "From here, from now on, Our Bright Parade",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:49.400",
        "end": "01:53.800",
        "original": "まだ 頼りない 横顔",
        "english": "Still an uncertain profile",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:54.200",
        "end": "01:58.500",
        "original": "歌を 恥ずかしくって 泣いた",
        "english": "I cried because I was embarrassed to sing",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:59.000",
        "end": "02:03.800",
        "original": "誰も 解けない 暇に",
        "english": "In a time that no one can unravel",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:04.100",
        "end": "02:08.600",
        "original": "いつか また 会える おまじない",
        "english": "A lucky charm to meet again someday",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:09.100",
        "end": "02:14.400",
        "original": "あの日 手のひらに 始まった ストーリー",
        "english": "A story that began in our palms that day",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:14.900",
        "end": "02:17.400",
        "original": "数えきれない 言の葉",
        "english": "Countless words",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:17.600",
        "end": "02:19.800",
        "original": "数えるような 思いじゃないさ",
        "english": "They aren't feelings you can just count",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:20.100",
        "end": "02:24.400",
        "original": "ほら 今 僕らを ひとつと 呼ぼう",
        "english": "Look, now let's call us one",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:25.500",
        "end": "02:29.800",
        "original": "パレパレパレ 美しいんだよ",
        "english": "Parade, parade, parade, it's beautiful",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:30.400",
        "end": "02:35.000",
        "original": "許し合える 切ない夜は 煌めく",
        "english": "Painful nights when we forgive each other sparkle",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:35.500",
        "end": "02:40.000",
        "original": "雨 晴れ カレ 待ってた空",
        "english": "Rain, sun, the sky we were waiting for",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:40.300",
        "end": "02:42.800",
        "original": "相応しい 旅路とは",
        "english": "What makes a worthy journey",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:43.000",
